<subSubSection pageId="75" pageNumber="1414" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="75.[178,1086,368,994]" pageId="75" pageNumber="1414">A d d i t i o n a l m a t e r i a l e x a m i n e d: Luzon, Lagunas Prov., Mt. Makiling, summit rd., 450-700 m, fungi on logs and in leaf and moss litter, 20-22. and 28.XI.19 95, leg. I. Löbl, 59 ex. (MHNG); Luzon, Lagunas Prov., Mt. Makiling, above Mad Springs, 400-700 m, 19-22.XI.1995, leg. J. Kodada, 5 ex. (MHNG); Luzon, Lagunas Prov., Mt. Makiling, 4 km SE Los Banos, 7. and 9.IV.1977, leg. L. Watrous, 9 ex. (MHNG); Luzon, Lagunas Prov., Mt. Banahaw above Kinabuhayan, 600-700 m, trail to Crystalino, 24-25.XI.1995, leg. J. Kodada &amp; B. Rigová, 16 ex., same but leg. I. Löbl, 10 ex. (MHNG, BZLA); Leyte, Visca N Baybay 100-200 m, 27.II.1991, leg. W. Schawaller, 6 ex. (SMNS, MHNG); Leyte, Lunay, 2.III.1913, leg. G. Böttcher, 1 ex. (ZMUB); Mindanao, Davao Prov., E. slope of Mt. McKinley, 3200 ft., 7-8.IX.1946, leg. F.G. Werner, 1 ex. (FMNH); Mindanao, Cotabato Prov., Burungkot, Upi, 1500 ft., 1-9.I.1947, taken on polypores and under bark, leg. F.G. Werner, 23 ex. (FMNH, MHNG); Mindanao, Cotabato Prov., 50 km N. of Parang, 500 ft., 6.XII.1946, leg. F.G. Werner, 7 ex. (FMNH, MHNG); Mindanao, Davao Prov., 25 km NW of New Bataan, 1200 m, 20-22.V.1996, leg. Bolm, 2 ex. (SMNS).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[178,731,847,869]" pageId="75" pageNumber="1414" type="distribution">
